{"tid":967584,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★賀！World No IT】Apple股價狂瀉近9%","createTime":"2019-01-03T15:03:43.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-04T00:45:32.000Z","uid":19454,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"dd4f0c028b98288e3f8d84ad171bd84edc9b8cf5","tid":967584,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-03T15:03:43.000Z","msg":"蘋果公司(Apple Inc.)罕有地發出收入預警，股價早段報144.03美元，挫8.8%，並拖累美股周四(1月3日)早段受壓，道指大幅低開306點，報23,039點；以科技股掛帥的納指亦瀉81點，至6,584點。<br />\n<br />\nApple將上季收入預測由原本介乎890億至930億美元，下調至約840億美元後，多家大行和券商隨即下調Apple目標價，當中，高盛將目標價由182美元降至140美元；加拿大皇家銀行相對樂觀，雖將Apple目標價由220美元降至185美元，但認為該股愈來愈接近具吸引力的估值。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/finance/20190103/bkn-20190103223154595-0103_00842_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Ffinance%2F20190103%2Fbkn-20190103223154595-0103_00842_001.html&d=bdENBHZHXM2N6cv0Qg04SwhMEkA7P3Wv%2FuCJwdwWxT4%3D&h=085bd1fe\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/finance/20190103/bkn-20190103223154595-0103_00842_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"5fffe3be2530d1d03dc6420137e62c255339a3cf","tid":967584,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-03T15:03:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e47484a1f1855dc55ef9d3c1505c294a52e81783","tid":967584,"uid":19454,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-03T15:04:20.000Z","msg":"no more smartphone please<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c2915df2ed760b2344f7323b11791062ffce1a41","tid":967584,"uid":76855,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-03T15:05:08.000Z","msg":"=.="},{"pid":"64a74031d82bc9f97b6f96d9fe5e3a0237c10a30","tid":967584,"uid":19454,"like"